1) emerge x11-libs/vte

Though you may need a newer version of vte, or you may not run gentoo so go here to get the vte sources:
ftp://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/sources/vte/

2) create a directory ~/.tilda and add a file config with the following lines

max_height=500
max_width=1600
min_height=1
min_width=1600

with your desired sizes. min_height cannot be less than 1.


3) gcc `pkg-config --cflags --libs gtk+-2.0` -lpthread -lvte -otilda src/tilda.c

4) ./tilda

5) ./tilda -T to move the terminal up and down
